{"tid":1077221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國隊沒進中國盃足球決賽 《央視》拒轉播被罵翻","createTime":"2019-03-25T12:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T14:31:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd9199feeac5245fc1045692130849fa6023103","tid":1077221,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpbS6rKf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpbS6rKf.jpg&h=2454daf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕2019年中國盃國際足球錦標賽3月21日展開，於廣西壯族自治區南寧市開踢，但中國隊當晚就提早被踢出局，無緣爭奪冠亞軍，《央視》也被球迷發現沒有進行決賽的轉播，被批毫無風度。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國男性足球隊於第3屆中國盃足球賽開踢當晚，就以1比0差距輸給泰國隊，確定不可能進入決賽，只能和中亞國家烏茲別克在25日角逐季軍賽，但依舊有球迷想要觀賞決賽賽事，卻在《央視》的節目表發現，只有季軍賽事轉播，沒有決賽可看。<br />\n<br />\n《央視》在決賽舉辦時，改轉播中國男子籃球職業聯賽（CBA）的賽況，不少中國網友認為該電視台不但失去地主之誼，也有輸不起的嫌疑；港媒指出，中國在被泰國隊打敗之後，在國際賽事累積的積分降低，目前亞洲第8的排名隨時都有可能被伊拉克奪走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2738440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2738440&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=87ec3754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2738440&h=b18df517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2738440</a>"},{"pid":"131246a815a0cf92b00602b9d3fd563abe53ee77","tid":1077221,"uid":234553,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"當無發生過"},{"pid":"45502b8aa0f02ef4a0618c1dd2e0b13b0737cacc","tid":1077221,"uid":42340,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee93d060940b487ca5658f05b19f36ef5be639c1","tid":1077221,"uid":1